BT 1 0 0 1 0 63 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The Wike Coherence Law, derived from quantum decoherence physics, governs the transition from organized to) Tj T* (disorganized states across every scale. Mark Granovetter published the threshold model of collective behavior in the) Tj T* /F3 9 Tf (American Journal of Sociology) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( in 1978. He identified that individuals have heterogeneous thresholds for joining collective) Tj T* (action, and that the distribution of these thresholds determines whether a riot ignites or fizzles. His threshold parameter is) Tj T* (mathematically identical to gamma_c -- the critical decoherence rate at which coherence undergoes sharp, irreversible) Tj T* (collapse.) Tj T* ET
